From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 11 Jun 2026 14:46:31 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Season-aware guidance, 2026 Collin roll failover, flood-zone
 fix, exemption check
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Data correctness (the big one for June use):
- Collin adapter now probes data.texas.gov resources newest-first
  (COLLIN_SOURCES: 'nne4-8riu' Preliminary -> 'vffy-snc6' 2025 certified)
  with its full field set, uses the first that answers, and caches the
  result for a day. The 2026 preliminary values are picked up the moment
  they are compatible, with automatic fallback if the schema drifts.
  Autocomplete shares the resolved resource so suggestions and lookups
  can never come from different roll years.
- Roll vintage (rollYear/rollLabel) now travels on SubjectProperty and is
  shown in the results card and both PDF headers; an amber warning appears
  from April onward when the data is from a prior tax year.

Season-aware guidance:
- protestSeason() (filing / hearing / planning) in constants.ts.
- 'How to file' is now 'What to do now': after May 15 it covers Sec. 41.461
  evidence requests, informal review, ARB hearing flow, late protest for
  good cause (41.44(b)), and Sec. 25.25(c)/(d) correction motions.
- The board packet's FILE step adapts the same way.

Flood zone on the happy path:
- Denton subject queries request the parcel centroid (outSR=4326), and
  run.ts falls back to a best-effort Census geocode (parallel with the
  comp fetch) for Collin — the FEMA lookup previously never ran when an
  autocomplete suggestion was picked, which is the main path.

Homestead exemption check (Denton):
- The already-fetched exemptions field is now surfaced: when no HS code is
  present and the cap isn't active, the results card suggests verifying /
  filing the exemption (free, retroactive up to two years).

Smaller wins:
- OpenGraph/Twitter meta tags for chat link previews.
- Safari/iOS-safe PDF download (delayed object-URL revoke).
- deploy.yml passes optional SOCRATA_APP_TOKEN secret to the build.

